									<h2>

							Find the Right Attorney
					</h2>

									<p>Motorcycle accident claims are not just “car accidents without doors.” Riders are often blamed automatically, with insurance companies assuming speeding, lane splitting, or reckless behavior. A strong case requires a lawyer who understands rider dynamics, common visibility issues, and the bias that many adjusters and juries have against motorcyclists.</p><p>AccidentLogic focuses on lawyers who regularly handle motorcycle cases, so they know how to counter these unfair assumptions from day one.</p>

